ข้อมูลภูมิแพ้

One of the most favourite coffee shops and hangout destinations in the bustling and energetic city of Bangkok, Coffee bean by Dao enjoys a loyal client following, thanks to its relaxing ambience, friendly services, and delicious cuisines and desserts. With six outlets in the heart of the city, this coffee shop, filled with tantalising aromas, is a wonderful place to have casual conversations while relishing your favourite treats. Coffee Bean by Dao menu features a stunning selection of food choices. However, the eatery is most celebrated for its scrumptious desserts that are certainly unmatched elsewhere in the city.

What's exciting in the acclaimed Coffee Bean by Dao menu?

Coffee Bean by Dao menu boasts an extensive selection of Asian and western delicacies. From vegetarian to non-vegetarian, you can find something unique and scrumptious for every taste. Hungry for a sumptuous meal? Then, indulge the traditional way by ordering Corn Soup with Crab Meat or Chicken Vegetable Soup. Veggies can opt for Mushroom Cream Soup. Next, treat yourself to the house specialities like Tasmanian Salmon with Balsamic Dressing, Crunchy Soft Shell Crab Meat, or Crispy Veg Spring Rolls. For main dishes, Southern Sour Yellow Curry Salmon with Rice & Thai Omelette, Stir-Fried Chicken & Eggplant Southern Style Curry & Salad, or Larb Glass Noodle & Mushroom are worth a try. If you prefer some classic items, then check out the Coffee Bean Platter Section, offering Chicken Stew, Chicken Parmesan Pizzaiola, Salmon Teriyaki, and Fish and Chips, amongst others. If are you in the mood for some refreshing bites, you could perhaps order Sauteed Mushroom with Garlic & Herbs, Chicken Liver Pate & Toast, and Tuna Cheese Sandwich & French Fries. The coffee Bean by Dao menu is full of surprises.

Famous desserts of Coffee bean Bangkok now at your doorsteps!

Walk into any one of the coffee bean outlets in the city, and the first thing that will grab your attention is the huge and luscious display of fresh pastries and cakes, mostly likely with a crowd in the front. The very sight of those fluffy sponge layered cakes with rich flavoured cream, topped with fruits, and chocolate sauce will make you drool. Know what, there is a whopping 70 unique varieties of cakes featured in the Coffee Bean by Dao menu. From classic cheesecakes, Chocolate Fudge, and Black Forest to local-inspired and exclusive Durian, Coconut Pandan Roll and Bael fruit cakes, Coffee bean by Dao menu will surely please the foodie in you! These fruit cake varieties are available only at the Coffee Bean by Dao menu. Carrot Cakes are also incredibly famous here. Another absolute must-try dessert on the Coffee Bean by Dao menu is the local delicacy Crepe Cake served with lip-smacking sauces. Tempted?! Craving to taste these mouthwatering delights right away? Simply order all these and much more dessert varieties and food choices via Coffee bean delivery services at foodpanda.
